title: Pizza & Chicken Empanadas Two flavors, because más is better! | 4-6 Servings
description: We’ve sent you two kinds of flaky, savory empanadas! Half are filled with seasoned chicken thighs and veggies, and the rest are filled with margherita pizza flavors (like tomato sauce, basil, and mozzarella cheese). These Latin American pastries are the perfect appetizer or snack for any mealtime or gathering. All you have to do is bake or air fry them to golden perfection and share! We like to dip them in sour cream and salsa, but feel free to serve them with your favorite dips and toppings.

