7.5 ounce Maspanadas Chicken Empanadas
7.5 ounce Maspanadas Pizza Empanadas

Keep refrigerated until ready to eat; best if used within 7 days.

OVEN: Adjust rack to middle position and preheat oven to 375 degrees. Place the empanadas on a lightly greased baking sheet. Bake on middle rack, flipping halfway through, until golden brown, 15-18 minutes. (Note: Oven times may vary.)

 AIR FRYER: Coat an air fryer basket with nonstick cooking spray. Arrange empanadas side by side in basket (you may have to work in batches). Air fry at 375 degrees until golden brown, 8-10 minutes.